quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,33,"Obuzibu bwe buba butuuse ku bantu basaba Mukama omulabirizi waabwe nga bamwemenyera, oluvanyuma bwabaloza ku kusaasira okuva gyali ogenda okulaba nga ekitundu ku bo bagatta ebintu ebirala ku Mukama omulabirizi waabwe"
  30,34,Kale beegaane ebyo bye twabawa era mweyagale mmwe (nabo) lumu mulimanya
  30,35,Abaffe oba twabawa obujulizi nga bwogera ku ebyo bye bagatta ku Katonda (nti bituufu)
  30,36,"Bwe tuba nga tulozezza abantu ku kusaasira kwaffe basanyuka nakwo, bwe baba nga batuukiddwako ekibi kyonna olw'ebyo e mikono gya bwe bye gyakola ogenda okulaba nga bakutuka n'okusuubira (okusaasira kwa) Katonda"
  30,37,"Abaffe tebalaba nti mazima Katonda agaziyiza eby'enfuna eri gwaba ayagadde ate naafundiza oyo gwaba ayagadde, mazima mu ekyo mulimu obubonero obulaga obuyinza bwa Katonda eri abantu abakkiriza"
  30,38,"Kale wa ow'olugandalwo olw'okumpi kyateekwa okuweebwa, n'omufuna mpola, n'omutambuze ekyo kye kirungi eri abo abaagala ebiri eri Katonda era abo bbo be bookutuuka ku kigendererwa"
  30,39,"Ekyo kyonna kye muba muwaddeyo (nga muwola) mu mmaali ey'ennyongeza (Riba) nti zigende zizaalire mu mmaali y'abantu tezizaala ewa Katonda, ate ekyo kye muba muwaddeyo mu Zzaka nga mwagala ebiri eri Katonda abo nno be basaanira ennyongeza"
  30,40,"Katonda yooyo eyabatonda bwamala naabagabirira bwamala naabatta, oluvanyuma agenda kubawa obulamu, abaffe mu bannammwe be mugatta ku Katonda waliwo akola ku ebyo ekintu kyonna? musukkulumu Katonda era yayawukana ku ebyo bye bamugattako"
  30,41,"Obwonoonefu bweyolese ku lukalu ne ku nnyanja olw'ebyo emikono gy'abantu bye gikola, (Katonda) alyoke abakombese ku bukaawu bw'ebimu ku ebyo bye baakola, balyoke beekomeko"